      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, an analog masterpiece of longitudinal front-midship engineering. This example features the high-revving F22C1 inline-four, delivering 240 hp with a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The close-ratio six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement with zero synchro hesitation. Mechanically flawless, the chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity thanks to the signature X-bone frame, complemented by a precise Torsen limited-slip differential and double-wishbone suspension at all four corners. This unit remains in showroom condition, with all original VIN tags intact and paint depth consistent across all factory panels. Recent comprehensive service includes a valve adjustment and fluid flush (trans/diff/coolant) to ensure peak thermal efficiency and drivetrain longevity.",
